                "Lyrics":"<a id=\"title\">HYMN #388</a><div id=\"content\">Today the Saviour calls:<br/>Ye wand'rers, come;<br/>O ye benighted souls,<br/>Why longer roam?<br/><br/>Today the Saviour calls:<br/>O listen now!<br/>Within these sacred walls<br/>To Jesus bow.<br/><br/>Today the Saviour calls:<br/>For refuge fly;<br/>The storm of justice falls,<br/>And death is nigh.<br/><br/>The Spirit calls today:<br/>Yield to his pow'r;<br/>O grieve him not away;<br/>'Tis mercy's hour.<br/><br/>AMEN.</div>",
