                "Lyrics":"<a id=\"title\">HYMN #424</a><div id=\"content\">I am trusting thee, Lord Jesus<br/>Trusting only thee:<br/>Trusting thee for full salvation,<br/>Great and free.<br/><br/>I am trusting thee for pardon;<br/>At thy feet I bow,<br/>For thy grace and tender mercy,<br/>Trusting now.<br/><br/>I am trusting thee for cleansing<br/>In the crimson flood;<br/>Trusting thee to make me holy<br/>By thy blood.<br/><br/>I am trusting thee to guide me;<br/>Thou alone shalt lead,<br/>Ev'ry day and hour supplying<br/>All my need.<br/><br/>I am trusting thee, Lord Jesus;<br/>Never let me fall;<br/>I am trusting thee for ever,<br/>And for all.<br/><br/>AMEN.</div>",
