                "Lyrics":"<a id=\"title\">HYMN #562</a><div id=\"content\">Father, whate'er of earthly bliss<br/>Thy sovereign will denies,<br/>Accepted at thy throne of grace,<br/>Let this petition rise:<br/><br/>Give me a calm, a thankful heart,<br/>From ev'ry murmur free;<br/>The blessings of thy grace impart,<br/>And make me live to thee.<br/><br/>Let the sweet hope that thou art mine<br/>My life and death attend;<br/>Thy presence through my journey shine,<br/>And crown my journey's end.<br/><br/>AMEN.</div>",
