                "Lyrics":"<a id=\"title\">HYMN #659</a><div id=\"content\">Father, we thank thee for the night,<br/>And for the pleasant morning light;<br/>For rest and food and loving care,<br/>And all that makes the day so fair.<br/><br/>Help us to do the things we should,<br/>To be to others kind and good;<br/>In all we do, in work, or play,<br/>To grow more loving ev'ry day.<br/><br/>AMEN.</div>",
