                "Num":"674",
                "Lyrics":"<a id=\"title\">HYMN #674</a><div id=\"content\">Holy Bible, book divine,<br/>Precious treasure, thou art mine;<br/>Mine to tell me whence I came;<br/>Mine to teach me what I am;<br/><br/>Mine to chide me when I rove;<br/>Mine to show a Saviour's love;<br/>Mine thou art to guide and guard;<br/>Mine to punish or reward;<br/><br/>Mine to comfort in distress,<br/>Suffering in this wilderness;<br/>Mine to show by living faith,<br/>Man can triumph over death;<br/><br/>Mine to tell of joys to come,<br/>And the rebel sinner's doom;<br/>O thou holy book divine,<br/>Precious treasure, thou art mine.<br/><br/>AMEN.</div>",
