                "Lyrics":"<a id=\"title\">HYMN #9</a><div id=\"content\">Hallelujah! Hallelujah!<br/>In his temple God be praised;<br/>In the high and heavenly places<br/>Be the sounding anthem raised.<br/><br/>Refrain:<br/>Hallelujah! Hallelujah! Hallelujah! Amen.<br/><br/>Hallelujah! praise Jehovah<br/>For his mighty acts of fame;<br/>Excellent his might and greatness;<br/>Fitting praises then proclaim.<br/><br/>Refrain:<br/>Hallelujah! Hallelujah! Hallelujah! Amen.<br/><br/>Hallelujah! praise Jehovah<br/>With the trumpet's joyful sound,<br/>Praise with harp and praise with organ,<br/>Let his glorious praise abound.<br/><br/>Refrain:<br/>Hallelujah! Hallelujah! Hallelujah! Amen.<br/><br/>Hallelujah! Hallelujah!<br/>All that breathe, Jehovah praise;<br/>Let the voices God has given<br/>Joyful anthems to him raise.<br/><br/>Refrain:<br/>Hallelujah! Hallelujah! Hallelujah! Amen.<br/><br/>AMEN.</div>",
