                "Lyrics":"<a id=\"title\">HYMN #29</a><div id=\"content\">Praise Jehovah, all ye nations,<br/>All ye people, praise proclaim;<br/>For his grace and lovingkindness,<br/>O sing praises to his name.<br/><br/>Great to us hath been his mercy,<br/>Ever faithful is his word;<br/>Through all ages it endureth.<br/>Hallelujah, praise the Lord.<br/><br/>AMEN.</div>",
                "FirstLine":"Praise Jehovah, all ye nations,",
