                "Num":"642",
                "Lyrics":"<a id=\"title\">HYMN #642</a><div id=\"content\">Jesus, tender Shepherd, hear me,<br/>Bless thy little lamb tonight;<br/>Through the darkness be thou near me,<br/>Keep me safe till morning light.<br/><br/>All this day thy hand has led me,<br/>And I thank thee for thy care;<br/>Thou hast clothed me, warmed and fed me,<br/>Listen to my ev'ning pray'r.<br/><br/>Let my sins be all forgiven;<br/>Bless the friends I love so well;<br/>Take me, when I die, to heav'n,<br/>Happy there with thee to dwell.<br/><br/>AMEN.</div>",
