                "Lyrics":"<a id=\"title\">HYMN #676</a><div id=\"content\">More about Jesus would I know,<br/>More of his grace to others show,<br/>More of his saving fullness see,<br/>More of his love who died for me.<br/><br/>Refrain:<br/>More, more about Jesus,<br/>More, more about Jesus,<br/>More of his saving fullness see,<br/>More of his love who died for me.<br/><br/>More about Jesus let me learn,<br/>More of his holy will discern;<br/>Spirit of God, my teacher be,<br/>Showing the things of Christ to me.<br/><br/>Refrain:<br/>More, more about Jesus,<br/>More, more about Jesus,<br/>More of his saving fullness see,<br/>More of his love who died for me.<br/><br/>More about Jesus in his Word,<br/>Holding communion with my Lord;<br/>Hearing his voice in ev'ry line,<br/>Making each faithful saying mine.<br/><br/>Refrain:<br/>More, more about Jesus,<br/>More, more about Jesus,<br/>More of his saving fullness see,<br/>More of his love who died for me.<br/><br/>More about Jesus on his throne,<br/>Riches in glory all his own;<br/>More of his kingdom's sure increase;<br/>More of his coming, Prince of Peace.<br/><br/>Refrain:<br/>More, more about Jesus,<br/>More, more about Jesus,<br/>More of his saving fullness see,<br/>More of his love who died for me.<br/><br/>AMEN.</div>",
