                "Num":"776",
                "Lyrics":"<a id=\"title\">HYMN #776</a><div id=\"content\">Breathe on me, breath of God,<br/>Fill me with life anew,<br/>That I may love what Thou dost love,<br/>And do what Thou wouldst do.<br/><br/>Breathe on me, breath of God,<br/>Until my heart is pure,<br/>Until with Thee I will one will,<br/>To do and to endure.<br/><br/>Breathe on me, breath of God,<br/>Till I am wholly Thine;<br/>Until this earthly part of me<br/>Glows with Thy fire divine.<br/><br/>Breathe on me, breath of God,<br/>So shall I never die,<br/>But live with Thee the perfect life<br/>Of Thine eternity.<br/><br/>AMEN.</div>",
